    "id": "activity-schema-correction-cannot-edit-activities",
    "severity": "HIGH",
    "category": "correctness",
    "location": "scripts/build/linear_pipeline.py:107",
    "description": "Adding activity_schema to WRITER_CORRECTION_GATES routes this failure through the existing writer-correction path, but that path renders a module.md-only prompt and accepts module.md-only patches for every gate except strict_json_parse. The activity_schema diagnostic points at activities.yaml item fields, yet the correction prompt explicitly forbids returning or patching activities.yaml, so an auto-correction retry cannot fix the failed gate and may instead rewrite module.md uselessly until the pipeline exhausts retries. This gate needs an artifact-aware correction path, or it should be excluded from WRITER_CORRECTION_GATES until corrections can modify activities.yaml."
  }
]

